# BACKSTAGE_ENTITY_NAME API

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### Info Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info

### OpenAPI Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs

### List All Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items

### List Active Items Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?activeOnly=true

### Get Item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1

### Search Items by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/search?name=Sample

### Create New Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "New Item",
    "description": "This is a new item created via API"
}

### Update Item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Updated Item",
    "description": "This item has been updated",
    "active": true
}

### Partial Update Item (only name)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Only Name Updated"
}

### Delete Item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1

### Create Multiple Items for Testing
